{"content":"    \n   <div class=\"LedgerScreen \"   id=\"LedgerScreen\" savrWidType=\"SCREEN\" >\n               <div class=\"LedgerScreen_Ledger\" savrWidType=\"RECT\" \n         >\n        \n                 <div class=\"LedgerScreen_Ledger_txt\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        Ledger\n        \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"img_LedgerScreen\"   savrWidType=\"IMAGE\"  >\n             \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"img_LedgerScreen_1\"   savrWidType=\"IMAGE\"  >\n             \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"img_imtt\"   savrWidType=\"IMAGE\"  >\n             \n      </div>\n      \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"Manage_Ledger_welcome\" savrWidType=\"RECT\" \n         >\n        \n                 <div class=\"Manage_Ledger\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        Manage Ledger\n        \n      </div>\n      \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"LedgerScreen_Summary_row\"    savrWidType=\"ROW\" >\n          <div class=\"savrintersub_LedgerScreen_Summary_row\" style=\"    display: flex; width: max-content; \n      gap: 2px 10px;\n    justify-content: flex-start;\n        align-items: center;\n    \">\n                     <div class=\"indicard\" savrWidType=\"RECT\" \n         >\n        \n                 <div class=\"img\"   savrWidType=\"IMAGE\"  >\n             \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"title\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        Net Income\n        \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"subtitle\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        $12,450.00\n        \n      </div>\n      \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"indicard_1\" savrWidType=\"RECT\" \n         >\n        \n                 <div class=\"img_1\"   savrWidType=\"IMAGE\"  >\n             \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"title_1\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        Net Expense\n        \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"subtitle_1\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        $8,210.00\n        \n      </div>\n      \n      </div>\n      \n          </div>\n        </div>\n               <div class=\"LedgerScreen_crow\" savrWidType=\"RECT\" \n         >\n        \n                 <div class=\"btn_New_Transaction\" savrWidType=\"RECT\" \n         >\n        \n                 <div class=\"btntxt_New_Transaction_text\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        New Transaction\n        \n      </div>\n      \n      </div>\n      \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"txt_Led\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        Recent History\n        \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"LedgerScreen_TransactionList\" savrWidType=\"grid_column\" \n          \n          >\n        \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"LedgerScreen_nav\" savrWidType=\"RECT\" \n         >\n        \n                 <div class=\"nav_Home\"   savrWidType=\"IMAGE\"  >\n             \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"LedgerScreen_Home_txt\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        Home\n        \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"nav_Ledger\"   savrWidType=\"IMAGE\"  >\n             \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"LedgerScreen_Ledger_txt_1\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        Ledger\n        \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"nav_Accounts\"   savrWidType=\"IMAGE\"  >\n             \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"LedgerScreen_Accounts_txt\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        Accounts\n        \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"nav_Journal\"   savrWidType=\"IMAGE\"  >\n             \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"LedgerScreen_Journal_txt\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        Journal\n        \n      </div>\n      \n      </div>\n      \n  </div>\n    ","code":"import traceback\nasync def run_main_savr():\n    try:\n        import ginni as g\n        import asyncio\n        \n        async def initialize_ledger():\n            # 1. Initialize Screen Text\n            # Updated title text color to blue (#3b82f6)\n            g.GinNode(\"LedgerScreen_Ledger_txt\").set_text_context(\"General Ledger\")\n            g.GinNode(\"LedgerScreen_Ledger_txt\").set_text_color(\"#3b82f6\")\n            g.GinNode(\"Manage_Ledger\").set_text_context(\"Review and manage your daily transactions.\")\n            # Updated welcome text color to blue as requested\n            g.GinNode(\"Manage_Ledger\").set_text_color(\"#3b82f6\")\n            \n            # 2. Styling the New Transaction Button\n            btn_new = g.GinNode(\"btn_New_Transaction\")\n            btn_new.set_color(\"#10b981\")  # Emerald Green\n            g.GinNode(\"btntxt_New_Transaction_text\").set_text_color(\"#ffffff\")\n        \n            # 3. Populate Transaction List with Realistic Data\n            transactions = [\n                {\"title\": \"Stripe Payout\", \"amount\": \"+$4,250.00\", \"type\": \"income\", \"icon\": \"https://img.icons8.com/color/96/stripe.png\"},\n                {\"title\": \"AWS Cloud Services\", \"amount\": \"-$154.20\", \"type\": \"expense\", \"icon\": \"https://img.icons8.com/color/96/amazon-web-services.png\"},\n                {\"title\": \"Office Supplies - Depot\", \"amount\": \"-$89.00\", \"type\": \"expense\", \"icon\": \"https://img.icons8.com/color/96/shopping-cart.png\"},\n                {\"title\": \"Consulting - Acme Corp\", \"amount\": \"+$1,500.00\", \"type\": \"income\", \"icon\": \"https://img.icons8.com/color/96/invoice.png\"},\n                {\"title\": \"Monthly Office Rent\", \"amount\": \"-$2,100.00\", \"type\": \"expense\", \"icon\": \"https://img.icons8.com/color/96/home.png\"}\n            ]\n            \n            for item in transactions:\n                # Clone the template for each entry\n                card = await g.create_widget_type(\"indicard_30\", \"LedgerScreen_TransactionList\")\n                card.get_child(\"title_30\").set_text_context(item[\"title\"])\n                card.get_child(\"subtitle_29\").set_text_context(item[\"amount\"])\n                card.get_child(\"img_24\").set_img_src(item[\"icon\"])\n                \n                # Set text color based on financial impact\n                if item[\"type\"] == \"income\":\n                    card.get_child(\"subtitle_29\").set_text_color(\"#10b981\")\n                else:\n                    card.get_child(\"subtitle_29\").set_text_color(\"#ef4444\")\n        \n            # 4. Implement Navigation for Bottom Bar\n            def navigate_dashboard(e): g.moveto(\"DashboardScreen\")\n            def navigate_accounts(e): g.moveto(\"AccountsScreen\")\n            def navigate_journal(e): g.moveto(\"JournalScreen\")\n            def navigate_ledger(e): g.moveto(\"LedgerScreen\")\n        \n            g.GinNode(\"nav_Home\").set_on_click(navigate_dashboard)\n            g.GinNode(\"LedgerScreen_Home_txt\").set_on_click(navigate_dashboard)\n            \n            g.GinNode(\"nav_Accounts\").set_on_click(navigate_accounts)\n            g.GinNode(\"LedgerScreen_Accounts_txt\").set_on_click(navigate_accounts)\n            \n            g.GinNode(\"nav_Journal\").set_on_click(navigate_journal)\n            g.GinNode(\"LedgerScreen_Journal_txt\").set_on_click(navigate_journal)\n        \n            g.GinNode(\"nav_Ledger\").set_on_click(navigate_ledger)\n            g.GinNode(\"LedgerScreen_Ledger_txt_1\").set_on_click(navigate_ledger)\n        \n            # 5. Implement New Transaction Button Functionality\n            async def handle_new_transaction(e):\n                async def on_submit(ev):\n                    g.show_toast(\"Transaction added to ledger successfully.\")\n                    g.close_overlay()\n                    \n                buttons = [\n                    g.Ginton(\"Save Transaction\", \"#10b981\", on_submit),\n                    g.Ginton(\"Dismiss\", \"#666666\", lambda ev: g.close_overlay())\n                ]\n                \n                g.open_drawup(\n                    title=\"Record New Entry\",\n                    details=\"Please enter the transaction amount, account source, and category tags for this ledger entry.\",\n                    buttons=buttons\n                )\n        \n            g.GinNode(\"btn_New_Transaction\").set_on_click(handle_new_transaction)\n            g.GinNode(\"btntxt_New_Transaction_text\").set_on_click(handle_new_transaction)\n        \n        # Safely execute the async initialization\n        asyncio.ensure_future(initialize_ledger())\n        pgst = g.GinNode('top-progress')\n        pgst.set_visibility(False)\n        g.print('ginniPageLoadMarker8900883612800000')\n    except Exception:\n       consolelogerror(traceback.format_exc())\n\nimport asyncio\nloop = asyncio.get_event_loop()\nresult = loop.run_until_complete(run_main_savr())\n       ","css":"          .LedgerScreen { background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); height: 100dvh; width: 100vw;  display:inline-block;overflow-y: scroll;overflow-x: hidden; flex: 0 0 auto;position: relative;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;} \n .LedgerScreen_Ledger { background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); height: 30px; width: 100%; box-shadow: none; text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;position: absolute;  top: 6px;} \n .LedgerScreen_Ledger_txt {white-space: normal;\n  word-wrap: break-word;\n  overflow-wrap: break-word; background: transparent; background-color: transparent; border: none; resize: none; color: rgba(28, 28, 30, 1); height: 30px; width: 120px; box-shadow: none; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  font-weight: 700;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;overflow-y: hidden;overflow-x: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis;position: absolute;  top: 6px;  left: 36px;} \n .img_LedgerScreen { background: rgba(28, 28, 30, 1); height: 14.399999999999999px; width: 14.399999999999999px; box-shadow: none; object-fit: cover; filter: invert(46%) saturate(2.78) hue-rotate(9deg) brightness(0.20) contrast(0.95); background-color: transparent; background-image: url('images/placeholders/Search.png'); text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:none;overflow: auto;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;position: absolute;  top: calc(50% + -9px);  right: 24px;} \n .img_LedgerScreen_1 { background: rgba(28, 28, 30, 1); height: 14.399999999999999px; width: 14.399999999999999px; box-shadow: none; object-fit: cover; filter: invert(54%) sepia(53%) saturate(3.12) hue-rotate(203deg) brightness(0.01) contrast(0.78); background-color: transparent; background-image: url('images/placeholders/Settings-sliders.png'); text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:none;overflow: auto;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;position: absolute;  top: calc(50% + -9px);  right: 44.4px;} \n .img_imtt { background: rgba(28, 28, 30, 1); height: 30px; width: 30px; box-shadow: none; object-fit: cover; filter: invert(15%) sepia(3%) saturate(2.94) hue-rotate(205deg) brightness(1.40) contrast(1.33); background-color: transparent; background-image: url('images/placeholders/Angle-small-down.png'); text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;position: absolute;  top: 6px;  right: 60px;} \n .Manage_Ledger_welcome { background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); height: 66px; width: 100%; box-shadow: none; text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;position: absolute;  top: 51px;} \n .Manage_Ledger {white-space: normal;\n  word-wrap: break-word;\n  overflow-wrap: break-word; background: transparent; background-color: transparent; border: none; resize: none; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); height: 60px; width: 100%; box-shadow: none; text-align: center; font-size: 18px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  font-weight: 600;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;position: absolute;  top: 12px;} \n .LedgerScreen_Summary_row { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); height: 174px; width: 100%; text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; white-space: nowrap;overflow-x: scroll;background: transparent; gap: 30px;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;position: absolute;  top: 132px;} \n .indicard { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); height: 150px; width: 150px; box-shadow: 0px 2px 4px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07); text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto; flex: 0 0 auto;position: relative;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 6px 6px 6px 6px;} \n .img { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); height: 60px; width: 60px; box-shadow: none; object-fit: cover; background-color: transparent; background-image: url('images/fc49e433-c842-43b8-aafe-48119b4ddb5a.png'); text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;position: absolute;  top: calc(50% + -69px);  left: 6px;} \n .title {white-space: normal;\n  word-wrap: break-word;\n  overflow-wrap: break-word; background: transparent; background-color: transparent; border: none; resize: none; color: rgba(28, 28, 30, 1); height: 36px; width: 87px; box-shadow: none; text-align: start; font-size: 18px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  font-weight: 800;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;overflow-y: hidden;overflow-x: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis;position: absolute;  top: 6px;  left: 69px;} \n .subtitle {white-space: normal;\n  word-wrap: break-word;\n  overflow-wrap: break-word; background: transparent; background-color: transparent; border: none; resize: none; color: rgba(28, 28, 30, 0.5882352941176471); height: 60px; width: 81px; box-shadow: none; text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  font-weight: 400;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;position: absolute;  top: 33px;  left: 69px;} \n .indicard_1 { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); height: 150px; width: 150px; box-shadow: 0px 2px 4px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07); text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto; flex: 0 0 auto;position: relative;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 6px 6px 6px 6px;} \n .img_1 { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); height: 60px; width: 60px; box-shadow: none; object-fit: cover; background-color: transparent; background-image: url('images/placeholders/Arrow-right.png'); text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;position: absolute;  top: calc(50% + -69px);  left: 6px;} \n .title_1 {white-space: normal;\n  word-wrap: break-word;\n  overflow-wrap: break-word; background: transparent; background-color: transparent; border: none; resize: none; color: rgba(28, 28, 30, 1); height: 36px; width: 87px; box-shadow: none; text-align: start; font-size: 18px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  font-weight: 800;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;overflow-y: hidden;overflow-x: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis;position: absolute;  top: 6px;  left: 69px;} \n .subtitle_1 {white-space: normal;\n  word-wrap: break-word;\n  overflow-wrap: break-word; background: transparent; background-color: transparent; border: none; resize: none; color: rgba(28, 28, 30, 0.5882352941176471); height: 60px; width: 81px; box-shadow: none; text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  font-weight: 400;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;position: absolute;  top: 33px;  left: 69px;} \n .LedgerScreen_crow { background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); height: 48px; width: 100%; box-shadow: none; text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;position: absolute;  top: 321px;} \n .btn_New_Transaction { background: rgba(255, 94, 0, 1); height: 24px; width: 192px; box-shadow: 0px 2px 4px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07); text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;border:0.6px solid rgba(255, 94, 0, 1);border-radius: 3px 3px 3px 3px;position: absolute;  top: 0px;  left: calc(50% + -102px);} \n .btntxt_New_Transaction_text {white-space: normal;\n  word-wrap: break-word;\n  overflow-wrap: break-word; background: transparent; background-color: transparent; border: none; resize: none; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); height: 19.2px; width: 192px; box-shadow: none; text-align: center; font-size: 9.6px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  font-weight: 600;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;overflow-y: hidden;overflow-x: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis;position: absolute;  top: 6px;  left: calc(50% + -96px);} \n .txt_Led {white-space: normal;\n  word-wrap: break-word;\n  overflow-wrap: break-word; background: transparent; background-c